Package polynomial

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Polynomial
    This class represents the methods to create a polynomial list.
    PolynomialNode
    This class represents a node of a polynomial list.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComparePower
    This class represents a function that will compare the degree of two polynomial terms.
    EvaluatePolynomial
    This class represents a function for evaluating the polynomial given the degrees and coefficients.
    PolynomialImpl
    This class represents a specific polynomial list.
    PolynomialNodeElement
    This represents a node for the list containing the polynomial.
    PolynomialNodeEmpty
    Represents an empty node of the polynomial list.
    PolynomialTerm
    This class represents an object that stores a single term of the polynomial.
